  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <br>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 13px 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 14px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: rgb(145, 145, 145);text-align: left;line-height: 1em;visibility: visible;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">作者 | 孟旭</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 13px 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 14px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: rgb(145, 145, 145);text-align: left;line-height: 1em;visibility: visible;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">编辑 | 李忠良</span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 13px 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 14px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: rgb(145, 145, 145);text-align: left;line-height: 1em;visibility: visible;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">策划 | AICon 全球人工智能开发与应用大会</span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"padding:19px;margin:24px 8px 0px;color:rgb(89, 89, 89);visibility:visible;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">在近期举办的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;AICon 全球人工智能开发与应用大会·上海站（2025）</span>现场，网易有道词典笔产品负责人孟旭以一款全新的 AI 原生硬件</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【有道 AI 答疑笔】</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">为例，分享了智能学习硬件在大模型技术催化下的变革逻辑——从解决单一需求的“学习工具”，进化为陪伴学习的“智能伙伴”。</span>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">孟旭指出，从多年的经验和认知出发，有道智能学习硬件的进化本质是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">用户需求、硬件创新与 AI 技术三者的螺旋推进，三者像齿轮一样咬合转动，推动产品进化</span>。即使是在大模型爆发的当下，纯软件升级或者纯硬件创新都更像是炫技，唯有软硬结合才能让技术润物无声地渗入场景，去解决用户的真问题 ，这也是垂类硬件在技术爆发时代的生存法则。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">以下根据演讲实录整理（部分内容有删改），供大家深入了解：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">大家好，我来自网易有道硬件产品团队，我叫孟旭。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">现在 AI 可以说无处不在了，作为智能学习硬件的产品团队，我们也一直在思考：当 AI 教育碰撞，如何让这项前沿技术真正成为孩子学习成长路上的\"智慧引路人”? 如何突破传统学习工具的局限，解决孩子在学习过程中遇到的实际痛点，为他们打造更高效、更沉浸、更个性化的学习体验?</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">今天我会以我们今年推出的全新品类——有道 AI 答疑笔——的创新点来展开说说，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">大模型催化下的 AI 学习硬件经历了什么样的变革</span>。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/355da209-7f36-42f7-d098-2c61eea05500/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6675925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100156530\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/355da209-7f36-42f7-d098-2c61eea05500/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">网易有道被大家熟知是因为有道词典、有道翻译官、有道云笔记等应用，所以我们在查词翻译、语言学习上有非常深的积累，而我们有道词典笔也在智能学习硬件领域深耕多年，今年年初有道词典笔累计销量突破了 1000 万台，这对于我们是一个里程碑，代表了这么多年超过千万的孩子和家长对我们的信任。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在这个过程中，我们发现学习硬件产品迭代过程呈现“需求牵引 - 技术支撑 - 体验升级”的螺旋式发展路径。即先由用户场景需求牵引，推动硬件创新和人工智能技术在产品中的应用；随着硬件和技术的提升，又为用户带来更好的使用体验，而新的体验又会催生用户更多、更高级的需求，如此循环往复，推动智能硬件不断向前演进。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">具体来说，</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n     <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d78a8abe-def5-45ba-e2bd-9d0e02db7a00/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">需求牵引</span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这是智能硬件发展的起点，也是核心驱动力。需求场景虽然会随着时代进行变化，但变化的路径和方向是有迹可循的。我们在最开始推出有道词典笔，解决的是在用户英语学习时候提供一个趁手的智能工具。基于有道词典在语言翻译方面积累了大量的专业数据，同时硬件技术能够实现扫描 - 识别 - 输出的快捷过程，词典笔就应运而生。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">后来，我们在大量用户的使用日志中发现，因为扫描翻译这个动作很方便，用户在学习中文遇到不懂的字词，也会习惯性的扫一下，所以我们紧接着丰富了扫描翻译的语种和内容，不光是双语的学习，还引入了小语种和古诗文的释义，乃至文言文的讲解。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">再接下来，我们又看到，随着孩子年龄的增长，会面临学习任务的升级，他们也会自然而然地想到，随手拿起词典笔能不能解决下数学、物理、化学这些学科问题，乃至能不能脱离桌面学习的空间，到随时随地都能够互动学习……这就是为什么从需求层面，我们会从词典笔扩展到 AI 答疑笔这个路径上来。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n     <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d78a8abe-def5-45ba-e2bd-9d0e02db7a00/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">硬件创新</span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当明确用户需求后，就需要通过硬件创新来实现。这涉及到材料科学、电子工程等多领域技术突破。例如，为了让有道词典笔更便于携带和操作，可能需要在保证性能的前提下，对其外观尺寸、材质进行优化；为了实现更快速的识别和处理速度，要升级芯片等硬件组件。同时，也要考虑规模化的成本问题。可以说，硬件创新是将用户需求转化为实际产品功能的关键环节。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <section style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\">\n     <span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 15px;height: 15px;background: none no-repeat center center;background-size: 100% 100%;margin-right: 10px;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d78a8abe-def5-45ba-e2bd-9d0e02db7a00/public&quot;);\"></span><span leaf=\"\">技术迭代</span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">人工智能技术为智能硬件注入了“智慧”灵魂。像图像识别技术能让词典笔精准识别文字；自然语言处理技术使其能够理解用户提问，并给出准确解答。人工智能技术的不断进步，如算法优化、深度学习能力提升等，为智能硬件实现更智能、更人性化的功能提供了技术支撑。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e11648a9-4d56-4ea2-3914-ed680f085700/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100156537\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e11648a9-4d56-4ea2-3914-ed680f085700/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">那今天，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">前沿的 AI 大模型和教育场景碰撞带来了什么新的变化呢？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">首先，在语言交互方面，大模型具有先天优势，尤其是在语言学习领域。有道早在 2023 年就在词典笔上落地并优化大模型，优先应用于翻译和多语言学习场景。大模型能够更好地理解自然语言，尤其是结合上下文，从而显著提升翻译的准确度、表达方式、情绪色彩和流畅度。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这里可以提一下，其实我们去年率先在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">行业内首次落地了端侧离线大模型</span>，主要用于中英离线翻译，团队还在推进文言文翻译和小语种翻译功能的开发。选择离线大模型的原因在于，许多孩子的学习场景中存在无网络或网络不稳定的情况，如学校、图书馆等，离线模型能够保证低延迟、高质量的学习体验，同时降低成本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">为此，有道定制了首颗 AI 芯片，提升芯片算力以满足大模型需求，同时实现超低功耗，满足孩子长时间使用不充电的需求。离线大模型的落地面临诸多挑战，如算力、内存、功耗和成本的限制，但团队成功实现了高质量的翻译，使得离线大模型翻译质量优于原有的 NMT 模型。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d11fcec1-820d-404d-8cfc-b2932fe7d900/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5722222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100156539\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d11fcec1-820d-404d-8cfc-b2932fe7d900/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">其次，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">推理模型展示了类真人的逻辑思考链</span>，在答疑辅导场景中进行应用，让 AI 更接近真人老师的讲解方式，实现了自然语言交互模拟一对一的对话过程，真正实现了教与学的双向交互。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">以我们自己的产品突破为例，在最新的有道 AI 答疑笔上，与传统基于题库的答疑方式不同，小 P 老师能够随时随地解答多学科、新题难题，不限制学科和题目来源，就像前段时间我们拿 AI 答疑笔试了下今年北京海淀的高考二模题，也能拿下不错的成绩，达到了清北分数线。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">同时，小 P 老师能够做到分步骤讲解解题思路，单独抽离知识点供用户追问，并提供举一反三的练习，包括真题练习和大模型生成的练习。并且，大模型的知识覆盖面直接拓展到了全学科领域，契合当下教育目标迈向学科融合发展的趋势，能够更好地承担起多学科高效辅助的角色。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这样，大模型解决了传统人力问题，孩子在学习过程中遇到问题可以随时获得精细化讲解，无需等待固定时段询问老师。此外，多模态技术的发展让有道 AI 答疑笔能支持多种交互方式，如扫描、拍照、语音等，也让用户能够拓展更多个性化学习体验，比如拍照朗读不同风格的文章、拍照自定义背单词等功能。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5a34144-7358-4731-4f3b-69bf9944c800/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5611111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 661px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100156541\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a5a34144-7358-4731-4f3b-69bf9944c800/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">可以看到，目前大模型应用已经能够解决一些以往产品没能很好解决的问题。但是如果看长远一点，我们认为下一个阶段可能是&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI Agent 和教育生态的深度融合</span>，也是我们正在探索的方向。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">随着孩子学习方式从以老师为中心转变为以学生为中心，以及从单一学科到多学科融合、从被动接受到主动探索的各种转变，传统学习工具的局限性愈发明显。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">比如，我们看到学生在预习课本的时候，就会探究课本以外的发散知识，有的孩子可能会好奇作者的生平，有的孩子可能会想了解文章的写作背景和故事等等，其实就是学习的个性化本质，也是教育的终极诉求。我们一直追求“因材施教”，但现在没有任何一个工具、一个产品能真正做到。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们也还在往这个方向去努力，哪个孩子不希望自己有个随身家教呢？所以我们一方面在答疑智能化上做功夫，比如让 AI 答疑笔可以根据你的“错题本”记录，提供更好的讲解；另外一个方面，是进一步提高产品层面端到端的成熟度，现在 AI 答疑笔里面有几十个应用，不同的应用处理不同的学习需求，比如背单词有专门的 APP，口语训练又是专门的 APP，然后课内同步学习又是不同的入口。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">那未来是不是能把这些散点功能串联成整个学习流程？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;clear:both;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">基于这样的构想，我们 AI 答疑笔一开始就是定位于 AI 原生智能硬件，软硬件相结合的自研系统具备集成的条件，或许未来能实现人、内容和流程的整合，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">当 AI Agent 解决孩子各类学习问题的时候，AI 答疑笔就能真正成为孩子专属的 AI 设备</span>。</span></p><section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "网易有道孟旭分享 AI 大模型如何驱动学习硬件从工具向智能伙伴转型，强调软硬结合与未来 Agent 方向。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "网易有道孟旭分享 AI 大模型如何驱动学习硬件从工具向智能伙伴转型，强调软硬结合与未来 Agent 方向。",
  "summary": "文章由网易有道硬件产品负责人孟旭在 AICon 大会上的演讲整理而成，探讨了 AI 大模型对智能学习硬件带来的变革。核心观点是学习硬件的进化是用户需求、硬件创新和 AI 技术螺旋推进的结果，尤其强调大模型时代软硬结合解决用户真问题的重要性。文章以有道 AI 答疑笔为例，阐述了大模型在语言交互（特别提到行业内首次落地**端侧离线大模型**，解决无网场景问题）、多学科答疑辅导、多模态交互等方面的应用突破，使其能提供更像真人老师的个性化、精细化讲解。同时展望了 AI Agent 与教育生态深度融合的未来，认为这将使学习硬件真正成为孩子的专属 AI 伙伴，实现“因材施教”的终极目标。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "学习硬件进化由需求、硬件和 AI 技术螺旋驱动",
      "explanation": "用户需求是起点，硬件创新是载体，AI 技术注入智慧，三者相互促进，推动智能学习硬件从解决单一问题向更智能伙伴演进。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大模型赋能学习硬件实现类真人答疑辅导",
      "explanation": "利用大模型的推理能力，学习硬件能像真人老师一样**随时随地解答多学科、新题难题，不限制学科和题目来源**，并分步骤讲解解题思路，提供个性化追问和举一反三练习，解决传统模式痛点。"
    },
    {
      "point": "软硬结合是 AI 技术在垂类硬件落地的关键",
      "explanation": "文章强调纯粹的技术或硬件创新不足以解决真问题，软硬件深度集成才能让 AI 技术无缝融入学习场景，提升用户体验。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI Agent 代表学习硬件未来的发展方向",
      "explanation": "未来学习硬件将整合各项功能，通过 AI Agent 实现端到端个性化、主动式学习，有望成为孩子的随身智能家教。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
